<br>
-Clattering Bone Neckalce will be your cheapest and easiest upgrade. I bought it for 1200pp on Torv and its a very good deal. I'd say 3k about right.<br>
<br>
- If ya like to quest the BoB (bracer) replace it with your SS bracers. It will give your more HP/sta less AC.<br>
<br>
- You may also want to upgrade your belt to the War Only belt dropped in CT. It exceeds your budget as it goes for about 40k on my server. Anyway, Camp it or save up for it its up to ya.<br>
<br>
My last suggestion is (not sure its 100% positive for you but I would go for it if I were you!)<br>
<br>
- Sell CoF =&gt; more plat - 80k (?)<br>
- buy Cloak of Maelstorm (will give you about 100hp) - 8k (?)<br>
- buy a haste belt such as RBB or RBG - 30k (?)<br>
- and you still have lots of plat left to upgrade other gears<br>
<br>
Clearly, you will have LESS Haste now. But if you can still hold aggro with LESS haste, why not! Another shopping list is <br>
<br>
- instead of buying Haste Belt, buy Siblisian Berserker Cloak (26% haste only though!! but with decent amount of HP) - 35k<br>
- Now your belt slot is free and can equip the belt from CT. - 40k<br>
<br>
Clearly, my last suggestion is debatable! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwandork.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 688<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/13/02 9:47:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3884.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_hp.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Need HP</span><hr size=1> haste &gt; 100hp<br>
